        Justine,
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    was as innocent as 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        I,
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    and she suffered the same 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        charge;
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    she died for 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        it;
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    and I am the cause of 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        this—I
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    murdered her. 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        William, Justine,&lt;pb xml:id="F1818_v3_097" n="093"/&gt;
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    and 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        Henry—they
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    all died by my 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        hands.”
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    &lt;p eID="novel1_letter4_chapter21_div4_div23_p3"/&gt; &lt;p sID="novel1_letter4_chapter21_div4_div23_p4"/&gt; My father had 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        often,
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    during my 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        imprisonment,
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    heard me make the same 
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_start"/&gt;
        assertion;
        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    when 
